  "transcription_segments": [
    {
      "id": "eab66d77-4727-4b7c-8938-38f80b4d24f0",
      "speaker_discord_id": "420362662208339968",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 0.0,
      "timestamp_end": 0.0,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:37:47.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:37:47.677000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "06974c43-1e63-4f3d-9721-42d38bdb6f41",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Antes tinha medo de estar jogando santo Cristo, era o que todos diziam quando ele se perdeu",
      "message_type": "ooc",
      "timestamp_start": 6.93,
      "timestamp_end": 9.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:37:54.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:37:57.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2020c055-3f84-4ffe-a904-f23fefdc8c79",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Deixou pra trás todo marasa da fazenda só pra assistir no seu sangue, o abdício subendeu",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 9.93,
      "timestamp_end": 12.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:37:57.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:00.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "ff3a10da-540e-4884-be52-7e89cb5ac362",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Quando vi a sobra, estava em ser mandrido ainda mais quando o contigo se soldava para o feio",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 12.93,
      "timestamp_end": 15.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:00.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:03.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "87bc7e64-9126-48fe-a3eb-2e51ce4032c0",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Era no terror da ser caninha onde morava na escola até o professor pulia e abriu",
      "message_type": "ooc",
      "timestamp_start": 15.93,
      "timestamp_end": 18.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:03.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:06.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "5e7accdf-3e04-4be8-913c-7c45a50aeb57",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Ia agir só pra roubar no isqueiro, e até a filha só colocava na caixinha do altar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 18.93,
      "timestamp_end": 20.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:06.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:08.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "ee7be90b-a5a3-4277-b9e1-3e2a033ac152",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja e Jockie",
      "text": "Sentia menos que era mesmo diferente, sentia que aquilo ali não era o seu lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 20.93,
      "timestamp_end": 23.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:08.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:11.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6f90ece8-5118-4975-b9b7-64954141022e",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Ele queria sair para ver o mar, as coisas que ele via na televisão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 23.93,
      "timestamp_end": 26.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:11.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:14.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "4b3dc2fc-02f7-4ff8-89b8-2c0eae094b88",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Juntou o chineiro para poder viajar, a escolha passou pela solidão",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 26.93,
      "timestamp_end": 29.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:14.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:17.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e0120f8e-7d6e-4c74-9c35-07c497d9af38",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Fabio",
      "text": "Comia todas as meninas, as cidades de santo, ilha de médicos, ou ser a professora",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 29.93,
      "timestamp_end": 32.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:17.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:20.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e9317b4e-ae4f-4a60-9c70-cfa82d6e2374",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Eles foram mandados pro reformatório, um dia mandou seu adjeto de tanto fio",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 32.93,
      "timestamp_end": 35.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:20.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:23.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "f73374bc-1c90-42a4-b3c7-279c428e4c3a",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Não entendia como a vida funcionava, a discriminação por causa dessa classe se movou",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 35.93,
      "timestamp_end": 38.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:23.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:26.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "9f280dc1-f8d0-40e5-aabc-9169b2c34415",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja e Jockie",
      "text": "Ficou engraçado de tentar achar respostas, comprou uma passagem, foi direto ao Salvador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 38.93,
      "timestamp_end": 40.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:26.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:28.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "3f0a91e3-45b9-4468-822c-a138d9457fae",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja e Jockie",
      "text": "Milha chegando, foi tomar um catecinho, encontrou um morreiro e me foi falar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 40.93,
      "timestamp_end": 43.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:28.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:31.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "be16566f-766d-4050-9dbd-d74bed5c3b4b",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "E foi até, eu tinha uma passagem, a pedra é a viagem, mas vou me salvar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 43.93,
      "timestamp_end": 46.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:31.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:34.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "87fd1260-7a23-4dcd-908f-853302e8d093",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "Butneja",
      "text": "Dizia a ele, estou indo pra Brasília, nesse país o lugar melhor não há",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 46.93,
      "timestamp_end": 49.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:34.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:37.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b5b213b8-0590-439e-a7b6-21ec565d0ad3",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": "null",
      "text": "Diz que só vou visitar a minha filha, eu fico aqui e você vai ao meu lugar",
      "message_type": "ooc",
      "timestamp_start": 49.93,
      "timestamp_end": 52.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:37.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:40.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "622580f8-6ca0-471f-aedf-89c561bad4e7",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Me esculpou uma cintura de pó, assim o ônibus entrou no planal sembral",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 52.93,
      "timestamp_end": 54.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:40.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:42.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1a867b16-b900-44ce-9b35-d5cc8628b34b",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Eles ficaram com a cidade saindo da rodoviária, viam a luz de natal",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 54.93,
      "timestamp_end": 57.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:42.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:45.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "25f3d0cd-76fe-41b0-94b4-4026e9e53c98",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Eu vi a outra cidade linda, a louva lua que começa a trabalhar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 57.93,
      "timestamp_end": 59.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:45.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:47.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "04ccfcdb-bf60-44a7-925b-586a489d7243",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Porta matéria, predígica, que eu ganhava pelo que ele tava de linda",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 59.93,
      "timestamp_end": 62.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:47.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:50.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "0731eda4-d194-44d0-83c1-4a1069ff59fa",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "A cintaria é a zona da cidade que gasta muito seu estilo de lábo, o trabalhador",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 62.93,
      "timestamp_end": 65.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:50.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:53.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "0c168f8b-7ce5-498c-8b74-bd7dc412709b",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "E conhecia a cidade que lhe dizia, já teve um negócio que o seu filho salvou",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 65.93,
      "timestamp_end": 68.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:53.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:56.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "92a74d12-956b-4e6a-b366-dbd0943da9b5",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "O primeiro ano que vivia na Bolívia, as outras casinhas de lá",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 68.93,
      "timestamp_end": 71.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:56.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:38:59.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "9872e822-013a-4091-af60-eb7d6680b3c8",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Seu nome era Fabio e ele dizia, que o negócio dele ia começar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 71.93,
      "timestamp_end": 73.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:38:59.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:39:01.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "0edd89a8-be89-49ca-893f-eab70938847c",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "As outras casinhas era mais trabalhado, mas o dinheiro não dava pra ele se alimentar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 73.93,
      "timestamp_end": 76.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:39:01.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:39:04.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf94d6-19de-402b-8408-5b90bae756dd",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Eu vi essa tia na zona de cidade que sempre dizia que o seu índice ia ajudar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 76.93,
      "timestamp_end": 79.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:39:04.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:39:07.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "421a9e94-33bf-44b2-b931-c78b5f6e08df",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Pois ele não queria, mas como ele se sentiu como um pau, ele queria se enviar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 79.93,
      "timestamp_end": 81.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:39:07.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:39:09.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "4b2f0abb-0251-499a-ae1a-27576f9fb813",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Elaborou mais uma vez o plano santo, mas é que se ficava a situação pra conversar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 81.93,
      "timestamp_end": 84.93,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:39:09.607000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:39:12.607000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "a9127884-f6bc-4657-b1ef-cae03bbbd19d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Essas palavras não querem passar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 143.66,
      "timestamp_end": 145.66,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:40:11.337000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:40:13.337000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "67976a55-f11b-4da9-837e-ac65ae15a044",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Não é só de descansar, é só de tirar ninguém do meio e não trabalhar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 300.0,
      "timestamp_end": 303.0,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:42:47.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:42:50.677000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "6a90eedd-cb70-49c1-913d-d824f3aef1c1",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Se me der oi no meio da minha vida, se eu não tinha um trabalho nesse lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 303.0,
      "timestamp_end": 306.0,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:42:50.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:42:53.677000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "25aee87c-c263-4fae-aab9-aca6b0e9d587",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Vou ocupar o que queria ou não queria ser, não tinha dinheiro, não queria se armar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 306.0,
      "timestamp_end": 308.0,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:42:53.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:42:55.677000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d2cf1b5e-3bb1-4fbf-afc6-8bb696fcbf29",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Vamos pra si, vamos pra toda a unição, que esteve de imploratina",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 308.0,
      "timestamp_end": 311.0,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:42:55.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:42:58.677000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "8dbb4331-2c73-4ceb-a5f6-7e03b858212d",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
      "speaker_character_name": null,
      "text": "Os que me trouxeram ali já deixaram de ir para esse lugar",
      "message_type": "ic",
      "timestamp_start": 311.0,
      "timestamp_end": 317.61,
      "timestamp_absolute_start": "2026-04-22T18:42:58.677000+00:00",
      "timestamp_absolute_end": "2026-04-22T18:43:05.287000+00:00",
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "uncertain_terms": []
    },
    {
      "id": "a11e4642-93ca-41cc-b816-d98cd105236b",
      "speaker_discord_id": "411916947773587456",
